<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bengali_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Sounds">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sounds">Sounds</span></h2>
<div class="rellink relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Bengali_phonology" title="Bengali phonology">Bengali phonology</a></div>
<p>The <a href="/wiki/Phoneme" title="Phoneme">phonemic</a> inventory of Bengali consists of 29 consonants and 14 vowels, including the seven <a href="/wiki/Nasalization" title="Nasalization">nasalized vowels</a>. An approximate <a href="/wiki/Phonetics" title="Phonetics">phonetic</a> scheme is set out below in <a href="/wiki/Help:IPA" title="Help:IPA" class="mw-redirect">International Phonetic Alphabet</a>.</p>
