<td>êe</td>
<td>nêe</td>
<td>she takes</td>
</tr>
<tr style="text-align:center">
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/æo̯/</span></td>
<td>êo</td>
<td>nêo</td>
<td>you take</td>
</tr>
