g" title="Bengali wedding">Wedding</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Bengali_people" title="Bengali people">Bengali people</a> (<a href="/wiki/List_of_Bengalis" title="List of Bengalis">list</a>)</span></p>
